# AxiusCharts Feature Audit — Gap Analysis vs LWC

## What AxiusCharts Has Today

| Area | Implemented |
|---|---|
| **Series** | Candlestick (OHLCV) only |
| **Volume** | Volume bars below candles |
| **Axes** | Price axis (right), Time axis (bottom), corner stub |
| **Grid** | Horizontal + vertical grid lines |
| **Crosshair** | Normal, Magnet, MagnetOHLC modes |
| **Interaction** | Pan, Zoom (wheel), Pinch zoom, Long-press, Touch tracking, Kinetic glide |
| **Drawings** | Trend line, Rectangle, Fibonacci retracement, Scale tool |
| **Data** | Apache Arrow columnar storage, LTTB downsampling, NaN/Inf sanitization |
| **Rendering** | WebGPU (primary) + Canvas2D (fallback), multi-canvas z-ordering, DPR-aware |
| **Formatters** | Basic price/time formatting |

---

## Missing Features (by priority)

### 🔴 Critical — Series Types

LWC ships **7 series types**. AxiusCharts only has candlestick.

| Series | LWC | AxiusCharts | Notes |
|---|---|---|---|
| Candlestick | ✅ | ✅ | Done |
| **Line** | ✅ | ❌ | Essential for overlays, indicators, price lines |
| **Area** | ✅ | ❌ | Line with gradient fill — very common |
| **Bar (OHLC)** | ✅ | ❌ | Traditional OHLC bars (no body, just ticks) |
| **Histogram** | ✅ | ❌ | Needed for MACD, volume profile overlays |
| **Baseline** | ✅ | ❌ | Area above/below a base price (P&L view) |
| **Custom Series** | ✅ | ❌ | Plugin API for user-defined series types |

---

### 🔴 Critical — Multi-Series & Multi-Pane

| Feature | LWC | AxiusCharts | Impact |
|---|---|---|---|
| **Multiple series on one pane** | ✅ | ❌ | Can't overlay MA/EMA on candles |
| **Multi-pane (stacked)** | ✅ | ❌ | Can't show RSI/MACD in separate panes |
| **Series API** (`addSeries`, `removeSeries`) | ✅ | ❌ | No dynamic series management |

---

### 🔴 Critical — Studies / Indicators

| Feature | LWC | AxiusCharts | Impact |
|---|---|---|---|
| **Indicator framework** | Plugin-based | Stub only | `studies/` module is empty |
| **Built-in indicators** (SMA, EMA, etc.) | Via plugins | ❌ | No indicators at all |
| **Indicator output rendering** | Line/Histogram/Area | ❌ | Blocked on missing series types |

---

