| **Logarithmic scale** | ✅ | ❌ |
| **Percentage scale** | ✅ | ❌ |
| **Indexed-to-100 scale** | ✅ | ❌ |
| **Multiple price scales** (left + right) | ✅ | ❌ |
| **Price scale inversion** | ✅ | ❌ |
| **Auto-scale margins** (configurable) | ✅ | Hardcoded |
| **Custom price formatters** | ✅ | Basic only |

