## Suggested Implementation Order

```mermaid
graph TD
    A[1. Line Series] --> B[2. Area Series]
    A --> C[3. Histogram Series]
    B --> D[4. Multi-Series Support]
    C --> D
    D --> E[5. Indicator Framework]
    E --> F[6. Built-in Indicators<br>SMA, EMA, RSI, MACD]
    D --> G[7. Multi-Pane]
    G --> F
    
    H[8. Real-time Updates] --> I[9. Price Lines & Markers]
    
    J[10. Log / % Scale] --> K[11. Event System]
    K --> L[12. Full API Surface]
```

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Line series** is the single biggest blocker — it unlocks overlays, indicators, price lines, and most advanced features. This should be the #1 priority.
